      "content": "没有让人失望",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "真的吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实第三期的时候有些失望了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "探案剧情有些太直给了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "看了开头就能想到他们接下来要给一个什么样的立意，要歌颂什么，批判什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得最简单的是第一季",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "红茶案，参天楼那些案子元素都太典型了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "看着总有些似曾相识之感",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "不准你说我的唐朝诡事录第一季！！！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "这是我的初心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "理解理解",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "那个时候古偶漫天飞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "唐朝诡事录第一集确实很惊艳",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "甘棠那一案挺好的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，有时恍惚一下，我真以为他们在拍聊斋",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "我一个人看会有点怕...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "刘家兄弟化的妆真的很像鬼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh有天我看的迷迷糊糊，睡着又醒来",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "家外下着雨，驿站里面也是阴雨连绵的样子",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "我乍一看还以为刘家兄弟是落水鬼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "笑死了，更像黑白无常好不好？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "21:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "黑白无常长得没那么阴险吧？（没见过黑白无常版",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "21:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh这么幽默你不要命啦？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "要的要的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "《我真的还想再活500年》",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，明天周末了，你要去玩嘛？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，我打算去看雪",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "苏州已经下雪了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "没啊，我去郊区山上看",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "好啊好啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你明天看雪应该要早起吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你要早点睡吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "绝无可能",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "明天周末，今天早睡，那我就亏了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "天才，真是天才！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "太会算账了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "那明天看雪前要准备的东西你都准备好了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "我就去郊区看个雪，要准备什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "帽子，手套？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "雪落在头发上很凉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "手套最好要买防水的，不然你打雪仗的时候雪球在手里化了，湿乎乎的很难受",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "我估计就我们南方这点小雪打不了雪仗吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "哈？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是在低估南方人看到雪的决心和冲动吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "别别别别别，你不是那种会玩南方小土豆梗的人吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "【擦汗】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "我讨厌的互联网梗有很多，南方小土豆排得上前三名",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "你把我当什么人了，我那么恶俗吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "再说了我也是南方人啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "我真的怕了，小土豆这个",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "也不是说你，是这个梗，太恶心了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "互联网上北方人对南方人的想象就好像是西方对中国的臆想",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "【汗流浃背了】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "精辟",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你的帽子手套准备好了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "我去看看嗷，家里有没有",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "好，去吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "明天别着凉了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "明天再和我说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "我预感明天你很忙，没空回信息",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "明天我也很忙",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
